\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_Stadium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Bolton_Stadium\"}, {\"begin\": 533, \"end\": 538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alloa\", \"score\": 0.9988053818704217, \"rank\": 0.001196046948800882, \"text\": \"Alloa\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alloa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alloa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marchand might not have been either.\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Duncan Scott got about as near to the 22-year-old as anyone else has during his staggering run of races this week.\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 773, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"score\": 0.9913273362707572, \"rank\": 0.004373974849644039, \"text\": \"Duncan Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Duncan_Scott_(swimmer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Scott becomes Scotland's most decorated Olympian  Scott shuns Sir Chris Hoy comparisons after Olympic gold  Scott is quiet man making a big noise  He beat the Frenchman in the semi-finals of this event on Thursday, but it is fair to say Marchand was holding a wee bit in.\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 1046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 775, \"end\": 780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.998097091123796, \"rank\": 0.0019065367221671719, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}, {\"begin\": 789, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9657614286694338, \"rank\": 0.03518863986809672, \"t