 those new bits of metal around.\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The home favourite uncorked the good stuff on Friday when it mattered though.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His third Olympic record in three finals this meet.\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The boy has something about him.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The guy is...\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did all right going head to head with him for a bit but that's rapid,\\\" Scott said of Marchand, who won by more than a second.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1381, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.998097091123796, \"rank\": 0.0019065367221671719, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}, {\"begin\": 1395, \"end\": 1403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999996918600593, \"rank\": 3.0639611830962394e-07, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's turned into an absolute world sensation.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From 2022 onwards, I knew he was going to be pretty good but what he has been able to do this week is amazing and it's inspirational.\\\"\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Scott has played this game for a while, though.\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1621, \"end\": 1626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.998097091123796, \"rank\": 0.0019065367221671719, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been to big events and has both the medals and the scars to show for it.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1748, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He swaggered out into this magnificent drum of noise with a gallus grin, licked his lips, made straight for Marchand's blocks, and gave them a shunt.\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1858, \"end\": 1866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999996918600593, \"rank\": 3.0639611830962394e-07, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then he had a poke around in his box.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A wee bit of mind games?\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why not.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Given how good the Frenchman is, the 27-year-old had to try something.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Eighth after the butterfly, Scott roared back to sit fourth after the backstroke.\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2073, \"end\": 2078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.998097091123796, \"rank\": 0.0019065367221671719, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His breaststroke took him up to second but the freestyle specialist could not do enough to overhaul Marchand down the last 50m.\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Scott swam his quickest time since the last Olympic final - just three-hundredths of a second outside the mark that earned him silver in Tokyo - but it was not enough for a first individual gold.\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2256, \"end\": 2261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.998097091123796, \"rank\": 0.0019065367221671719, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}, {\"begin\": 2393, \"end\": 2398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9998638610295527, \"rank\": 0.00013615750677586599, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All the latest on the Scottish athletes at the Olympics  What to expect from the Scots on Saturday at the Olympics  It was sufficient, though, to earn him the title of Scotland's most decorated Olympic athlete, with his two gold and six silvers taking him beyond cyclist Sir Chris Hoy.\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2534, \"end\": 2539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"score\": 0.8545449225608697, \"rank\": 0.1702134933201758, \"text\": \"Scots\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_people\"}, {\"begin\": 2621, \"end\": 2629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9657614286694338, \"rank\": 0.03518863986809672, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2728, \"end\": 2737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Hoy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Hoy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Scott - while thrilled with his night's work - was not having any of that talk, though.\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I mean...\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2839, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I should not be in the same sentence as that guy or Andy Murray,\\\" he told BBC Scotland.\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2892, \"end\": 2903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.408189674478683e-47, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2914, \"end\": 2926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9999998338376055, \"rank\": 1.661622688428764e-07, \"text\": \"BBC Scotland\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Those two have been a huge inspiration to everything I have done.\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sure, I have got a few medals but I could not have got this many without being part of a load of fantastic relays.\\\"\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3112, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Might there be more of those relays to come over the next couple of days?\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3187, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite not planning to have them in his schedule for this meet, Scott is now keen for a role in either the mixed or men's 4x100m medley.\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3254, \"end\": 3259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.998097091123796, \"rank\": 0.0019065367221671719, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hoy's mark might not only be beaten, but eclipsed entirely by Sunday night.\", \"from\": 3327, \"to\": 3402, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am always going to throw my hand up,\\\" said Scott, after embracing his Saltire-wielding family in the stands as the cameras cut to the aforementioned Murray amid the crowd.\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3450, \"end\": 3455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.998097091123796, \"rank\": 0.0019065367221671719, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}, {\"begin\": 3556, \"end\": 3562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5032760772434627e-17, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just love racing in these environments and it brings something special out of me.\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Back-to-back silvers in the 200m IM is pretty cool and what a night it's been.\\\"\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fifa set t